docs {
  ## Submit BLS To Execution Changes

  Submit signed BLS to execution change messages to the beacon node to be broadcast to the network.

  ### Request Body
  Array of signed BLS to execution change objects, each containing:
  - `message`: BLS to execution change data (validator_index, from_bls_pubkey, to_execution_address)
  - `signature`: BLS signature

  ### Response (200)
  BLS to execution changes are stored in the pool and broadcast to the network. Returns 200 on success.
}
